<h2>The Unisex Challenge</h2>
<p>Most watches are marketed as strictly men’s or women’s, but the Tissot Everytime Medium refuses to pick a side. At $172.93, this Swiss-made quartz watch is designed to look good on anyone regardless of wrist size or style preference.</p>

<h2>Clean Minimalism</h2>
<p>The Everytime collection is named after the concept of timelessness, and the design reflects that. Clean dial, minimal branding, simple stick markers — nothing about this watch will look dated in five, ten, or twenty years.</p>

<h2>Swiss Heritage at an Entry-Level Price</h2>
<p>Tissot has been making watches since 1853. The Everytime Medium is one of the most affordable ways to put a Swiss-made watch on your wrist.</p>

<h2>Perfect Gift Potential</h2>
<p>Because it works for everyone, the Everytime Medium is the perfect gift for someone who values quality over flashy branding.</p>
